{"tid":33592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日 特首選委會選舉 投票日","createTime":"2016-12-11T02:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T11:38:51.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a91c5234926247e11af54adbbef7a40edd287968","tid":33592,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T02:05:33.000Z","msg":"特首梁振英日前宣佈不參選競逐連任，令特首戰況產生劇變。選委會選舉今日舉行，投票時間為早上7時半至晚上10時半。截至今早8時半，累積投票人數為1,899人，投票率為0.82%，較上屆0.32%為高。<br />\n<br />\n今屆共有25個界別需要競逐，共1239名候選人角逐733個席位，連同早前自動當選的400多人，合共近1200人會負責選出下屆行政長官。23萬多名選民今日會投票選出選舉委員會25個界別分組中的733席選委，負責選出下屆行政長官。"},{"pid":"7ab7d698dc248be61b3307df73050ae87388e048","tid":33592,"uid":23215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T02:19:34.000Z","msg":"已投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：IT狗"},{"pid":"3ec67e2996baffc17fd94ef2f7dacbff2ea7730a","tid":33592,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T02:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：IT狗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIT狗，你的選票很有用"},{"pid":"2abd75ed30e60341e96b707a0640a220dd966c7c","tid":33592,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T02:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b1f566bfc8d1f2a4b07dd4be4a8c3d5940601b","tid":33592,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T02:27:33.000Z","msg":"食完早餐投<br />\n<br />\n利申 都係IT狗"},{"pid":"67c5a06aa2710c72865bb6e33fffc18091133ac5","tid":33592,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T02:36:44.000Z","msg":"有票既一定要去投呀"},{"pid":"f6bd038181522634b7a660d3cf1cb1028fb2f4e9","tid":33592,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T02:38:53.000Z","msg":"而家兩大八婆爭，泛民咪又係投返白票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces